    static void PatternCompress.FFT​(java.util.List<ISymbol> ls)
    regarding the concept it is a little bit like fft for mp3, but we will speak about periodicity instead of frequency, occurency instead of amplitude the periodicity is the distance between 2 times that a symbol happen. the occurence is the number of times where this periodicity happens. * the goal is to catch the periodicity that happen the more often for all symbol to find the structure of the file. after we extract a pattern with fix field, and variable area.
